                <h2 class="section-heading">About me</h2>
                <p>My name is Luís Carlos Freitas Pinto. I was born on April 26, 1985 in the city of Chaves and from an early age I try to fulfill my dreams.</p>
                <p>I learned that nothing in life comes easily and good education and respect make us better people. I discovered the importance of fighting for what you want and dream, I do it every day. Today I consider myself a determined, focused and persistent person. I believe that the future will be even better and that gives me more willpower to pursue it.</p>
